{"tid":2374762,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"印度疫苗生產商興建中廠房大火　或影響疫苗增產","createTime":"2021-01-21T12:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T13:03:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92d6b4e4e734156b5bc6fc60cf02232fd08f5345","tid":2374762,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:58:16.000Z","msg":"全球產量及銷售劑量最高的疫苗商印度血清研究所，一座正在興建的廠房發生大火，現存的5千萬劑疫苗及儲存設施，未受影響，但可能影響擴大疫苗生產的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n起火的廠房位於印度西部城市浦那，現場圖片顯示，廠房冒出大量濃煙，消防員到場撲救，暫時未清楚起火原因及廠房受破壞的程度。<br />\n<br />\n公司表示，大火只影響正興建的新設施，有關設施用作增加疫苗產量，對現存疫苗未有影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571646-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571646-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=1a05ff24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571646-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c1bc196a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571646-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b005f1f8233a70b6ca700850972719087b83cd61","tid":2374762,"uid":76804,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:59:32.000Z","msg":"deep state又想阻止世界回復正常"},{"pid":"7ac1d994ac8d4e10f321c2ac88c3df003c25a345","tid":2374762,"uid":89182,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"Deep state 又陷害咖喱手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c8a5bccea7aca1552d497c848a7f45a5a2cb49","tid":2374762,"uid":276679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92d6b4e4e734156b5bc6fc60cf02232fd08f5345","tid":2374762,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:58:16.000Z","msg":"全球產量及銷售劑量最高的疫苗商印度血清研究所，一座正在興建的廠房發生大火，現存的5千萬劑疫苗及儲存設施，未受影響，但可能影響擴大疫苗生產的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n起火的廠房位於印度西部城市浦那，現場圖片顯示，廠房冒出大量濃煙，消防員到場撲救，暫時未清楚起火原因及廠房受破壞的程度。<br />\n<br />\n公司表示，大火只影響正興建的新設施，有關設施用作增加疫苗產量，對現存疫苗未有影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571646-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571646-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=1a05ff24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571646-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c1bc196a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571646-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:01:39.000Z","msg":"信政府！唔驚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065019b55e5525c3fcf42a3b1821710a4d352323","tid":2374762,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}